1
00:00:01,972 --> 00:00:04,453
Metta Bhavana, developing goodwill.

2
00:00:06,815 --> 00:00:10,378
Don't be concerned if during the exercise loving feelings don't arise.

3
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:16,364
Here we're concerned with attitude, developing an attitude of goodwill, metta.

4
00:00:17,925 --> 00:00:20,327
If pleasant emotions do arise, all well and good.

5
00:00:20,687 --> 00:00:25,352
If not, the exercise is still working for us and eventually the heart will respond.

6
00:00:27,152 --> 00:00:31,336
Remember you can stop the tape any time and develop a part of it further.

7
00:00:33,292 --> 00:00:37,317
So make sure you're now sitting in a comfortable position and feel free to move.

8
00:00:38,057 --> 00:00:41,482
So long as you move slowly, it won't disturb your concentration.

9
00:00:45,847 --> 00:00:46,529
So let's begin.

10
00:00:46,588 --> 00:00:55,401
Bring to mind someone you have a warm regard for, not connected to erotically or romantically.

11
00:00:56,182 --> 00:00:56,502
Better.

12
00:00:57,743 --> 00:01:00,226
An old friend, friend of the family, and so on.

13
00:01:01,118 --> 00:01:23,007
and offer them some worldly blessings good health long life prosperity whatever's appropriate and we can offer them some spiritual blessings

14
00:01:24,203 --> 00:01:32,850
May you be free of greed and selfishness, hatred and ill-will, fear and anxiety, ignorance and delusion.

15
00:01:34,212 --> 00:01:38,615
May you be kind and gentle, sympathetic and benevolent.

16
00:01:39,617 --> 00:01:41,978
May you be forgiving and compassionate.

17
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:46,582
May you be joyful and rejoice in the success of others.

18
00:01:48,164 --> 00:01:50,025
May you be peaceful and calm.

19
00:01:50,947 --> 00:01:53,569
May you be liberated of all your sufferings

20
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:58,135
may you experience the peace and bliss of Nibbana.

21
00:02:03,304 --> 00:02:18,324
Allowing those images to fade away, sensing that goodwill in our hearts, and bring to mind all those who are near and dear to us, offering them worldly blessings.

22
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:36,989
May you be free of greed and selfishness, hatred and ill will, fear and anxiety, ignorance and delusion.

23
00:02:37,909 --> 00:02:42,054
May you be kind and gentle, sympathetic and benevolent.

24
00:02:42,854 --> 00:02:45,677
May you be forgiving and compassionate.

25
00:02:46,959 --> 00:02:50,222
May you be joyful and rejoice in the success of others.

26
00:02:51,622 --> 00:02:53,444
May you be peaceful and calm.

27
00:02:54,866 --> 00:02:57,288
May you be liberated of all your sufferings.

28
00:02:58,298 --> 00:03:20,155
may you experience the peace and bliss of nibbana allowing those images to fade away and bring to mind friends people at work whomever we wish offering them worldly blessings

29
00:03:34,731 --> 00:03:43,504
May you be free of greed and selfishness, hatred and ill will, fear and anxiety, ignorance and delusion.

30
00:03:44,948 --> 00:03:48,933
May you be kind and gentle, sympathetic and benevolent.

31
00:03:50,014 --> 00:03:52,758
May you be forgiving and compassionate.

32
00:03:54,301 --> 00:03:57,747
May you be joyful and rejoice in the success of others.

33
00:03:59,128 --> 00:04:00,991
May you be peaceful and calm.

34
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:04,723
May you be liberated of all your sufferings.

35
00:04:05,844 --> 00:04:09,449
May you experience the peace and bliss of Nibbāna.

36
00:04:15,158 --> 00:04:25,072
Allowing those images to fade away and turning the stream of compassion inward towards ourselves, let's offer ourselves some worldly blessings.

37
00:04:37,810 --> 00:05:04,711
May I be free of greed and selfishness May I be free of hatred and ill will May I be free of fear and anxiety May I be free of ignorance and delusion May I be kind and gentle, sympathetic and benevolent May I be forgiving and compassionate

38
00:05:06,245 --> 00:05:10,531
May I be joyful and rejoice in the success of others.

39
00:05:12,593 --> 00:05:14,435
May I be peaceful and calm.

40
00:05:16,779 --> 00:05:19,223
May I be liberated of all my sufferings.

41
00:05:21,084 --> 00:05:24,990
May I experience the peace and bliss of nirvana.

42
00:05:31,579 --> 00:05:34,564
Having generated now this goodwill within our hearts,

43
00:05:34,865 --> 00:05:38,375
let's begin to radiate it outwards.

44
00:05:38,396 --> 00:05:45,920
First of all, to those immediate to us, in our household, in our group, offering everyone worldly blessings.

45
00:06:02,911 --> 00:06:11,238
May we be free of greed and selfishness, hatred and ill will, fear and anxiety, ignorance and delusion.

46
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:16,723
May we be kind and gentle, sympathetic and benevolent.

47
00:06:18,086 --> 00:06:20,327
May we be forgiving and compassionate.

48
00:06:21,288 --> 00:06:25,112
May we be joyful and rejoice in the success of others.

49
00:06:26,653 --> 00:06:28,555
May we be peaceful and calm.

50
00:06:28,615 --> 00:06:32,800
May we be liberated of all our sufferings

51
00:06:33,725 --> 00:06:41,817
May we experience the peace and bliss of Nibbana.

52
00:06:41,836 --> 00:06:52,172
Continuing to raid it outwards till we've covered the whole of our area or town or city, offering everyone the good and bad alike worldly blessings.

53
00:07:08,166 --> 00:07:16,937
May you be free of greed and selfishness, hatred and ill will, fear and anxiety, ignorance and delusion.

54
00:07:18,339 --> 00:07:23,927
May you be kind and gentle, sympathetic and benevolent.

55
00:07:23,947 --> 00:07:26,209
May you be forgiving and compassionate.

56
00:07:27,190 --> 00:07:30,454
May you be joyful and rejoice in the success of others.

57
00:07:32,096 --> 00:07:34,038
May you be peaceful and calm.

58
00:07:34,930 --> 00:07:37,413
May you be liberated of all your sufferings.

59
00:07:38,415 --> 00:07:41,759
May you experience the peace and bliss of Nibbana.

60
00:07:46,007 --> 00:07:52,516
Continuing to read it outwards till we've covered the whole of our country, offering everyone worldly blessings.

61
00:08:09,423 --> 00:08:17,610
May you be free of greed and selfishness, hatred and ill will, fear and anxiety, ignorance and delusion.

62
00:08:19,192 --> 00:08:24,696
May you be kind and gentle, sympathetic and benevolent.

63
00:08:24,716 --> 00:08:26,918
May you be forgiving and compassionate.

64
